# 🚀 3. Space Mission Update – Rover & Exploration Missions

Recent rover missions (like those on Mars and the Moon) rely on:

* autonomous navigation
* real-time hazard detection
* high-efficiency embedded computing
* ADCS-based orientation systems

These missions demonstrate:

* the future of planetary exploration
* advances in onboard AI
* stronger embedded autonomy
* lightweight, efficient hardware for long-duration missions


